1. d4
{ In this chapter, we'll take a look at a variety of opening tactics. The opening tactics are all from the trainable lines, frequently from blue clickables, and generally involve a mistake by Black. They're categorized into Easy, Medium, and Hard. Some are quite trivial, but many will surprise you and some will be very hard without knowing the theme. For pedagogical reasons I've given them before the trainables so you can puzzle a bit over the right solution yourself. However, you can also leave the hard ones after you've trained the lines, if you want to. }
