Be3 Bd6 9. Ne5 g6 10. g4 Ng7 11. h4 Nxe5
{ Black's second and very natural option is to take the bait and grab the pawn  (~45 games)  . }
12. dxe5 Bxe5 13. h5 { We push on. The threat is h6, trapping the knight. }
13... gxh5
