[Result "*"]

1. d4
{ This was a Classical game. White was rated 2602 and Black was rated 2439. }
1... Nf6 2. Bf4 d5 3. e3 c5 4. Nf3 Nc6 5. Nbd2 e6 6. c3 cxd4 7. exd4 Nh5 8. Be3
Bd6 9. Ne5 g6 10. g4 Ng7 11. h4 Nxe5 12. dxe5 Bxe5 13. h5 O-O 14. f4 Bf6 15.
hxg6 fxg6 16. Nf3 { This is where we ended our trainable line. } 16... e5 17.
Nxe5 Qe7
{ This is, in fact, a mistake.   17...Ne6  This is the engine suggestion. } 18.
Qxd5+ Be6 19. Qe4
{ 19.Qg2  Engine chess.  19...Bxe5  20.fxe5  Rad8  21.Qh2  Ne8  22.Be2  White's up a pawn with the two bishops and really in no big danger. }
19... Bh4+ { This check just allows White's king to run to c2. } 20. Kd2 Rad8+
21. Kc2
{ Now White is already practically winning with a  completely safe king. }
21... Nf5 22. Rh3 { Best move!   22.gxf5??  Bxf5 } 22... b5 23. Bg2
{ 23.Bxb5  White could've just grabbed the pawn with the idea to play Bc4 next. }
23... Nd6 24. Qb4 Bf6 25. Rah1
{ Again, best move. White really wants to use the h-file. He's already completely winning. }
25... a5 26. Qc5 Bxa2 27. Rxh7 Qe6 { Hoping to drum up counterplay... } 28. Qc7
{ Threatening mate with Rh8+ and Qh7#. } 28... Nf7
{ 28...a4??  Just to demonstrate.  29.Rh8+  Bxh8  30.Qh7 } 29. Nxf7 Rd7
{ 29...Qb3+  30.Kc1  White's king is safe on c1. } 30. Qc5
{ Here White missed a variation on the previous idea, the crushing...   30.Rh8+  Bxh8  31.Rxh8+  Kxf7  32.Rh7+  Kg8  33.Rxd7 }
30... Rdxf7 31. Rxf7
{ This gives away a lot of the White advantage.   31.R7h6 } 31... Rxf7 32. f5
Bb3+ 33. Kc1 Qd7
{ Black blunders.   33...gxf5  34.gxf5  Qe5  Was necessary and the game is almost equal. }
34. fxg6 Re7 35. g5
{ 35.Bc6!  Qe6  36.Bd4  Bxd4  37.Qxd4  Qe3+  38.Qxe3  Rxe3  39.Bxb5  White's just winning. }
35... Re5 36. gxf6 { Oh yeah! } 36... Rxc5 37. Bxc5 Qd3 38. f7+ Bxf7 39. gxf7+
Kxf7 40. Rf1+ Ke6 41. Re1+ Kf7 42. Bd4
{ Black's Queen is helpless against White's two bishops and rook. } 42... b4
43. Bf1 Qf3 44. Bc4+ Kg6 45. Kc2 bxc3 46. Bxc3 a4
{ Final mistake, but it was over anyway. } 47. Bd3+ Kg5 48. Bd2+ Kh4 49. Re4+ *

