7... Qxa2 8. Ra1 { Forcing the Queen back to  b2  . } 8... Qb2 9. Rxa6
{ Removing the defender of c7. } 9... bxa6 10. Nc7+ Kd8 11. Ng5
{ Black's only way of surviving this is  11...Qb4+  12.Qd2  Qb1+  13.Ke2  and even then White is a lot better. }
