{ This is a completely new move, which hasn't been played. White "simply" pins the Queen, not minding ...e5. }
9... cxd4
{ 9...e5  Let's check.  10.e4  It looks dangerous with Black's Queen facing our king...  10...exd4  11.O-O !  Now we're already threatening Bxc6 and e5.  11...dxc3  12.bxc3  Ne5  13.Bxd7+  Qxd7  14.exd5  O-O-O  15.c4  With a huge edge for White. }
10. exd4 O-O 11. O-O Qd8 { Black has nothing better to get his king out. } 12.
Re1
