1... Nf6 2. Bf4 d5 3. e3 c5 4. Nd2 e6 5. Ngf3 Nc6 6. c3 Bd6 7. Bg3 O-O 8. Bd3
b6 9. e4 Be7 10. e5 Nh5 11. Ng5 Bxg5 12. Qxh5 g6 13. Qe2 cxd4 14. h4 Bh6 15. h5
dxc3 16. bxc3 Bg7 17. f4
{ This was also Stoovflees's choice in this position. } 17... Qc7 18. Nf3
{ 18.h6  White can also install the thorn pawn here. } 18... d4 19. Rc1
