{ This bishop is now basically a dead piece and won't see the light of day until the end of the game. }
22. Kf2
{ 22.O-O  White could also just castle.   22.Bh4  could've been considered as well. }
22... Qb8 23. Rhc1
{ Despite being a pawn down White has a clear positional edge here. } 23... Nb4
{ The main point of this move is to play ...Nd5. } 24. Kg1
