{ 20...Bxf1?  Doesn't work.  21.Rg3+  Kh8  22.Qh5  White threatens Nf7+ and after the rook is gone, Bxf6+ is the big threat.  22...f4   22...fxe5  23.Bxd8  Raxd8  24.Qh6  Rf7  25.exf5  exf5  26.Qe6  23.Nf7+  Rxf7  24.Qxf7  fxg3  25.Bxf6+ }
21. Rg3+ Kh8 22. Qh5 { The Queen enters with deadly effect. } 22... Be8 23. Qh6
{ The threat is Rg6!! } 23... Nc6 24. Nxc6 Bxc6 25. e5
{ Black resigned since Bxf6+ is coming and after Rxf6, exf6, White has Rg7. } *

