{ Since Black's knight is still at home White should clarify the central structure immediately. }
5... exd5 6. e3 { White can also start with  6.Qb3  . } 6... Nf6 7. Qb3
{ White attacks the bishop and forces a capture, retreat, or, most likely and best, ...Nc6. }
7... Nc6 { If  7...Bxc3+  8.Qxc3  . } 8. Ne2
