6. Nb5 e5
{ The most played move here.  6...Qa5+  7.c3  e5  8.Nxe5  Transposes. } 7. Nxe5
Qa5+ 8. c3 c4 { This is mostly tried, but it doesn't work. } 9. Nxc4
