Nf6 2. Bf4 g6 3. Nc3 d5 4. e3 Bg7 5. h4 c6 6. Be2 h5 7. Nf3 O-O 8. Qd2 Nbd7 9.
Ne5 Nxe5 10. Bxe5 b5 11. f3 a5 12. O-O-O a4 13. a3 { Stopping ...b4. } 13...
Qb6 { Insisting on ...b4. } 14. Na2 { Once more, stopping ...b4. } 14... Bf5
15. Bd3 Bd7 { Better was  15...Bxd3  . } 16. g4
