{ The rarest of the one-pawn moves. Black prevents Nb5 and could be preparing ...c5. }
6. Be2
{ Simplest and most thematic, fortifying the threat of  h5  . I will give the sharper, but unclear  6.h5  , intending the rook sacrifice, as an alternative. }
6... h5 7. Nf3 O-O 8. Ne5 c5 { Black follows his plan. } 9. dxc5
