1... Nf6 2. Nc3 d5 3. Bf4 g6 4. e3 Bg7 5. h4 a6 6. h5 Nxh5 7. Rxh5 gxh5 8. Qxh5
{ White is attacking the d-pawn and Black can't allow Nxd5 so he has to defend it somehow. }
