18. Re1 Qg5+ 19. Kb1 f5 20. dxe6 { Even better was  20.Qc5  . } 20... O-O 21.
a4 { Trying to deflect the b-pawn. } 21... Re8
{ If  21...bxa4  22.e7  Re8  23.Qd4  with the threat of  Bc4+  . } 22. axb5
axb5 23. Bxb5 Re7 { Black tries to get to the a-file. } 24. Bc4 Kg7 25. Qd4+
Kg6 26. g4
