1... e6 2. Bf4 c5 3. e3 Qb6 4. Nc3 Nf6 5. Rb1
{ We arrive at our position from a different move order. } 5... cxd4 6. exd4
Bb4 7. Nf3 O-O 8. Bd3 Qa5 9. O-O { White does not care about the b-pawn. } 9...
Bxc3 10. bxc3 { This looks dangerous for Black. } 10... d5
