13. Qe3 e6 14. Ne5
{ A blunder, after which the game is equalish. White could've won with  14.Na5!  Qa6  15.Bc7!  b6  16.Rg5   Or  14.Na5!  Qc3  15.Nc4  d5  16.Be5  Ng4  17.Bxc3  Nxe3  18.Nxe3 }
14... Qa6 { Draw agreed. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
