5... Ne4
{ We trained   5...d4  6.exf6  dxc3  7.Qe2+  and   5...Qe7  6.Qe2  d4  6.exf6  Qxe2+  7.Ncxe2  as tactics. This is another option for Black. }
6. Nxd5 d6
{ If Black tries a hail-mary with  6...Qh4  simply  7.Be3  and all is good. }
7. Qe2 { Black will lose more material. } *

