9. h3 { Prophylaxis against any future ...Bg4 or ...Ng4-e5 ideas. } 9... Rb8
{ The most common move, preparing the ...b5 break. If something like  9...b6  10.Bf4   or  9...b6  10.Re1   or  9...b6  10.Qd3  with thematic play. }
10. a5
