1. d4
{ In this chapter, you will find the rest of the model games. Most games collected here follow our trainable lines for some while, but usually feature a deviation for White or an alternative line, while being still instructive.  The games have been arranged in the order of the chapters: first you'll get a few games in the Exchange Caro-Kann, then Tricky 4...Qb6, 5...Bf5, 5...Bg4, then Sharp 5...Qb6 and so on. }
